{"tid":1605290,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非入黎!!!唔好再話行街look發夢!幫手帶物資出街!!保護好自己!!","createTime":"2019-09-30T08:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T15:57:09.000Z","uid":256046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9dca9055c230cf9c4e18edd060dc7913913d486d","tid":1605290,"uid":256046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:49:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">和理非出黎發夢都有好多野可以幫手!<br />\n</span></span><br />\n唔好同我講行街look就咩都唔帶<br />\n唔好以為淨係個人行出黎嗌下口號就幫到手<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">好多野可以帶出黎支援前線:</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">每個人帶少少就好多架啦!!!</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">長遮</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">索帶，最好粗既</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">士吧拿</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">六角匙</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">剪刀</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">勞工手套</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">水，生理鹽水</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">替換衫</span></strong></span><br />\n（呢幾日發夢，個人覺得前線比較需要索帶，六角匙同士吧拿起rb。）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">每人幫手帶少少出黎就多好多物資架啦</span><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: large;\">幫手印定啲文宣攞出黎貼，帶噴漆噴字，做人鏈幫手傳物資，幫手開遮遮住前線拆鐵搬鐵</span></em><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">所有人都要保護好自己!<br />\n全黑基本野<br />\n戴帽戴面巾口罩<br />\n唔好諗住淨係戴個口罩就認你唔到<br />\n買返條面巾遮埋耳仔同頸<br />\n無面巾既可以學下用件深色既tshirt包住<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A26y5B0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA26y5B0.jpg&h=6b253429&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，聽日10月1號，全民攝衫，賀佢老母<br />\n各位加油，小心!"},{"pid":"09ea684e39415965a0d6e5db89482f6c546ce0d3","tid":1605290,"uid":256046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T11:27:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a340753e0b72629696b44b9b7a2d0d7ae875cb8","tid":1605290,"uid":256046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:56:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d86f63cfaf440692a592c59d1ce55a00ab12396d","tid":1605290,"uid":256046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:57:09.000Z","msg":"一推再推"}]}